{"data":[{"id":562755561,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562755561","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546142406,"updated_time":1546142406,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":8,"content":"\u003cp\u003e瓜还没熟透，闲聊几句…\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e网络上嘲讽之声不绝于耳，还编出了各种类似问题…不是说不能质疑题主的能力，但是他的证明还没公布就冷嘲热讽，这种现象和题主吊众人胃口一样，都不是什么值得鼓励的事情…\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我只是觉得题主真正让人嗤鼻的是他故意卖关子…（阿提亚爵士也做过这事，但他是在会议上公布，合情合理啊…）当然，这一举动也说明，他还不是个民科，因为后者巴不得尽早得到他人认可，尤其是金字塔顶端那些人的认可，而题主却想把证明先丢给金字塔中下层的这群人…这么看来，他不过是个不懂事的孩子…\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这件事里，孩子没有孩子的样子，大人也没有大人的样子…但孩子终究是孩子，他的时间还长的很，还有大把机会纠正错误…大人们呢…\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一次说了这么多人，匿名了…\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560409728,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"67691aba48c2079e75deed5ffd14cd30","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560409728","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545835497,"updated_time":1545835497,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":8,"content":"\u003cp\u003e太过分的嘲讽也该停止了吧\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562355739,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562355739","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546077903,"updated_time":1546077903,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e进清华北大的方式千千万，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e为什么非要选择这样一条死路呢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e跳跳健美操啥的也能保送进去啊。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过说到美，我就想起了美猴王孙悟空，今年下半年中美合作的哥德巴赫猜想就要开机了，题主继续扮演孙悟空，他会努力创造一个搞笑的形象，文体两开花，弘扬高等数学文化，希望大家多多关注。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560642537,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"2c640cf6872c33ea1ef6a2832c371e9c","url_token":"he-qi-wei-53","name":"人民的气味362","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/2c640cf6872c33ea1ef6a2832c371e9c","user_type":"people","headline":"准大学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560642537","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545876200,"updated_time":1545926123,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":39,"content":"让我们来猜一下最后的结果：\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eA.新型炒作\u003cbr\u003eB.天才出道\u003cbr\u003eC.哗众取宠\u003cbr\u003eD.年轻自大\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e看了很多回复，我坚定地支持B\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e------------------------------\u003cbr\u003e（补充）本人粗俗的见解：\u003cbr\u003eA.如果是炒作，批评那个少年有什么意思？矛头好像对错地方了吧？\u003cbr\u003eC.如果是哗众取宠，适度教育一下就行了吧？\u003cbr\u003eD.如果是年轻自大，一个批评的刺激就够大了，上千批评聚在一起，给别人带来的心理创伤会有多大？万一别人想不开了，不会有点点愧疚吗？\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e选B的用意不言而喻。","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560428559,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"59ccae35512aa06a3eee4fd5c5f3c5d6","url_token":"lu-dian-12","name":"鲁殿","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/59ccae35512aa06a3eee4fd5c5f3c5d6","user_type":"people","headline":"学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560428559","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545837005,"updated_time":1545837327,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":8,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我觉得这个同学敢作敢当，即使错了又怎么样呢？为什么要有这么多恶意呢？这些传播恶意的又有多少对高中数学一窍不通的呢？嗯？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e又有多少是为了取笑而取笑的呢？是为了找乐而找乐的呢？至少他对于一个问题有探索精神 也看得出来对数学很热爱，而那些找乐的又有多少连一道普通的高中证明题都做不出来的呢？不管证明是浮皮潦草还是考虑欠周，我认为至少应该给人家公正的待遇，如果你说不出他证明的哪里不对，请不要取笑，请不要找乐 ，就当是为了一个孩子的数学梦，好吗？我真的希望可以少一点恶意，真的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果他真的出错了，我也希望大佬们可以认真的纠正，但是我还是希望取笑讥讽不屑的声音可以少一些\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然了，对于某一些单纯为了找乐而找乐的知识水平不高的人，我说这个无疑是对牛弹琴\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我只是希望，大家可以给这个孩子一点尊严，即使错了，我希望可以你们说的更多的是让他不要再骄傲，不要再急于求成，要善于遮蔽锋芒，要沉浸下去\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e毕竟高中生是最青春的那些人了，如果正确引导，至少以后他再遇到这样的人，不会是加以嘲笑，而是善于引导，往往一个孩子成为魔鬼还是天使全在咱们这些旁观者。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一直在关注校园暴力，其实我觉得，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e网络暴力，比校园暴力更能摧毁一个人。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563039572,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"dfa64433a84d681a333659bfccf83f3f","url_token":"zi-ming-47-37","name":"梓茗","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-89596e9248bef7858b583cc21b97ffd5_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-89596e9248bef7858b583cc21b97ffd5_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/dfa64433a84d681a333659bfccf83f3f","user_type":"people","headline":"知乎小透明。","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563039572","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546175721,"updated_time":1546175721,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e如果有个人真的能证明，不论你是小学生、初中生、高中生、校区老大爷，北大清华都会“保送”你成为教授。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e反正我高中的时候，有段时间挺膨胀，觉得自己理科还可以，有一次在新华书店，看陈景润和1+2的相关书籍，看了5分钟，完全没有任何头绪，那时候我知道，我这辈子不是学数学的料。我只是一个普通人。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e高考数学最后一道题的解题思路，在这种世界难题和解题大神面前连“易证”的级别可能都达不到，都是直接写答案的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e想来我到初中，还偶尔做做这样的梦。不经意证明了哥德巴赫猜想，回家妈妈给我做了糖醋排骨，还给我买了一双新的篮球鞋做为奖励。美滋滋。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e(●—●)\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562646940,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"79a2c2975d8dd0af4b324b22b35d4058","url_token":"zhu-ce-17-70","name":"I-邽山穷奇","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-11619b5f707bb2bbf3aeb9b0dc817561_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-11619b5f707bb2bbf3aeb9b0dc817561_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/79a2c2975d8dd0af4b324b22b35d4058","user_type":"people","headline":"男儿何不带吴钩，收取关山五十州","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562646940","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-46c36bf68daade52dc436e97373d2c37_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546129939,"updated_time":1546142265,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e耽搁我期末考试的时间吃瓜\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e要是瓜不甜，我就打死你\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-46c36bf68daade52dc436e97373d2c37_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"685\" data-rawheight=\"734\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-abf58eb62dc15075360d832b54945666_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"685\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-46c36bf68daade52dc436e97373d2c37_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='685'%20height='734'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"685\" data-rawheight=\"734\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-abf58eb62dc15075360d832b54945666_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"685\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-46c36bf68daade52dc436e97373d2c37_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-46c36bf68daade52dc436e97373d2c37_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e正经说的话\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个有伟大成就的人\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先是一个有敬畏之心的人\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他知道那些光辉闪耀的知识凝聚着多少伟人的智慧与努力\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后踏着前人的足记，心怀敬畏，探索未知\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e用题主所说的初等数学（高一高二）去证明哥德巴赫猜想\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e要么哗众取宠\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e要么坐井观天\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560809298,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"edb63ca6d0e2d62dc6b3085c8c216aa8","url_token":"liu-ze-pei-19","name":"Jeanskon Lowsan","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-f32399d5fa19776f708f4eb6debfe982_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-f32399d5fa19776f708f4eb6debfe982_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/edb63ca6d0e2d62dc6b3085c8c216aa8","user_type":"people","headline":"get the fuck up","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560809298","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545889